node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Saint Hoax on August 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Benjamin Hulett @benjaminhulett Peop shouldn't say the US war against Afghanistan was "all for nothing" as if there could have been a noble or justified result. It was all for profit; it was for defense contractors like Lockheed Martin & private companies who use death as a means to accumulate capital.'.

Photo by Saint Hoax on August 16, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Sana Jamal @Sana_Jamal Millions of lives lost. Decades of endless US wars in Iraq, Syria, Libya, Vietnam, Afghanistan. Yet the cycle of conflict and destabilization strategy continues. Insanity is doing the same thing over and over and expecting different results.'.

Being a 51-year-old Harvard-educated person who only realized using homophobic slurs was a bad thing *months* ago; and 2. Being foolish enough to think that was a cute story he should share with the world.'.
